         - heading \"Changes\" [level=2] [ref=e257]\n                    - list [ref=e258]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e259]:\n                        - strong [ref=e260]:\n                          - code [ref=e261]: src/config/types.slack.ts\n                        - text: \": Add\"\n                        - code [ref=e262]: requireExplicitMention\n                        - text: to\n                        - code [ref=e263]: SlackThreadConfig\n                      - listitem [ref=e264]:\n                        - strong [ref=e265]:\n                          - code [ref=e266]: src/config/zod-schema.providers-core.ts\n                        - text: \": Add field to\"\n                        - code [ref=e267]: SlackThreadSchema\n                      - listitem [ref=e268]:\n                        - strong [ref=e269]:\n                          - code [ref=e270]: extensions/slack/src/monitor/context.ts\n                        - text: \": Thread the new option through\"\n                        - code [ref=e271]: SlackMonitorContext\n                      - listitem [ref=e272]:\n                        - strong [ref=e273]:\n                          - code [ref=e274]: extensions/slack/src/monitor/provider.ts\n                        - text: \": Read config and pass to context\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e275]:\n                        - strong [ref=e276]:\n                          - code [ref=e277]: extensions/slack/src/monitor/message-handler/prepare.ts\n                        - text: \": Gate\"\n                        - code [ref=e278]: implicitMention\n                        - text: on the new flag\n                      - listitem [ref=e279]:\n                        - strong [ref=e280]:\n                          - code [ref=e281]: extensions/slack/src/config-ui-hints.ts\n                        - text: \": Add UI hint\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e282]:\n                        - strong [ref=e283]:\n              