{"type":"message","id":"8b85cb32","parentId":"fac92943","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:24:18.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw 每日资讯已生成完成 🎉\n\n已完成今日资讯采集和文章生成，内容包括：\n\n1. **Bug 追踪**: Browser 插件方法注册问题已确认，社区开发者上报\n2. **近期合并 PR**: 3 个最新合并的代码提交（功能更新、依赖升级、bug 修复）\n3. **项目数据**: 最新的 GitHub 星标和分支数据\n\n文章已保存到 `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260407.md`，任务状态已更新为 `completed`。\n\n---\n\n**今日资讯摘要：**\n- 社区上报 Browser 插件方法注册问题，目前正在调查中\n- Codex ACP 会话新增 detached head 选项，方便代码评审\n- ClawHub 技能同步元数据解析问题已修复\n- 项目星标突破 350k 🎊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1236,"output":211,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25823,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775521454917,"responseId":"02177552145510367b4ef5ba44a9620b39cdc0042b313b3572cfb"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"38be23f3","parentId":"8b85cb32","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:30:13.121Z","summary":"## Goal\nCheck the workspace heartbeat per instructions, check for any pending tasks in the task directory\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must read `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md` (exact case), do not read `docs/heartbeat.md`\n- Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- (none)\n- [x] Attempted to read `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks` (got expected error `EISDIR: illegal operation on a directory, read` for a directory read)\n- [x] Listed directory contents of `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/`\n- [x] Read the most recent task file `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json` and confirmed it is already completed\n- [x] Searched all task JSON files for pending tasks, found no pending tasks\n- [x] Confirmed no pending tasks need attention, replied HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n### In Progress\n- (none)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **No pending tasks found**: Confirmed all existing daily tasks are completed, so replied HEARTBEAT_OK per instructions\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Await new user instructions\n\n## Critical Context\n- Current check time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 4:22 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 20:22 UTC\n- The most recent task `openclaw_daily_20260406.json` (search OpenClaw latest news and generate a WeChat public account article) is already marked as completed\n- No tasks with `\"status\": \"pending\"` were found in `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/*.json`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nThe user instructed to read the specified HEARTBEAT.md file, follow any pending tasks, and handle current workspace heartbeat processing. A pending daily news task was found: generate a WeChat official account article covering the latest 7-day OpenClaw news, save it to the `wechat_articles/` directory with a date-named filename.\n\n## Early Progress\n1. Found the pending task: `openclaw_daily_20260407.json`\n2. Two `web_search` attempts both failed with a 401 Kimi API authentication error\n3. Confirmed the `wechat_articles/` directory exists and contains past daily OpenClaw news articles, including the most recent one from April 6, 2026\n4. Git log checks failed as neither the workspace nor parent directory is a git repository\n5. Read the April 6, 2026 past article to reference its format\n6. Attempted multiple web access methods to get latest OpenClaw updates from GitHub: `web_fetch` failed, then a browser instance was opened to access the OpenClaw repository, and navigated to multiple recent pull request pages.\n\n## Context for Suffix\nMultiple browser snapshots of GitHub pages were captured, but only the header navigation content is visible so far; the actual PR/commit content needed to extract latest OpenClaw news is still truncated and needs to be accessed. The goal remains to collect 2-3 latest valuable OpenClaw updates and write the styled daily news article for April 7, 2026.\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260407.json\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"518182de","tokensBefore":25823,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260407.json","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
{"type":"message","id":"1e594244","parentId":"38be23f3","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:30:13.158Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-07 08:30:00 GMT+8] 🔔 每日定时任务：检查并执行 OpenClaw 每日资讯推送任务\nSystem: \nSystem: 请执行以下步骤：\nSystem: 1. 检查 /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/ 目录下是否有今天的 pending 任务 openclaw_daily_YYYYMMDD.json\nSystem: 2. 如果有任务，按照任务 instructions 和 steps 执行：搜索 OpenClaw 最新资讯，生成微信公众号文章，保存到 wechat_articles/ 目录\nSystem: 3. 完成后将文章发送到钉钉群 cidUNAfzlz+0GntERJWlrGXIw==\nSystem: 4. 更新任务状态为 completed\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\n🔔 每日定时任务：检查并执行 OpenClaw 每日资讯推送任务\n\n请执行以下步骤：\n1. 检查 /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/ 目录下是否有今天的 pending 任务 openclaw_daily_YYYYMMDD.json\n2. 如果有任务，按照任务 instructions 和 steps 执行：搜索 OpenClaw 最新资讯，生成微信公众号文章，保存到 wechat_articles/ 目录\n3. 完成后将文章发送到钉钉群 cidUNAfzlz+0GntERJWlrGXIw==\n4. 更新任务状态为 completed\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 08:30 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 00:30 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775521813121}}
