{"type":"message","id":"250249e4","parentId":"943dd713","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:31:39.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 每日资讯推送任务已完成！\n\n- ✅ 文章已生成并保存到 `wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260407.md`\n- ✅ 已成功推送到钉钉群 `cidUNAfzlz+0GntERJWlrGXIw==`\n- ✅ 任务状态已更新为 `completed`\n\n今日资讯内容要点：\n1. 社区上报 Browser 插件方法注册问题，正在调查中\n2. Codex ACP 会话新增 detached head 选项，方便代码评审\n3. ClawHub 技能同步元数据解析问题已修复\n4. OpenClaw GitHub 星标已突破 350k 🎊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1964,"output":158,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775521859918,"responseId":"021775521860134beb22b84618335a214e9b1bc67d5e6c39a88d9"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"a2a8a3fe","parentId":"250249e4","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:01:29.401Z","summary":"## Goal\nCheck the workspace heartbeat per instructions, check for any pending tasks in the task directory; complete the found pending daily task: generate a WeChat official account article covering the latest 7-day OpenClaw news, save it to the `wechat_articles/` directory with a date-named filename\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must read `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md` (exact case), do not read `docs/heartbeat.md`\n- Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- (none)\n- [x] Attempted to read `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks` (got expected error `EISDIR: illegal operation on a directory, read` for a directory read)\n- [x] Listed directory contents of `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/`\n- [x] Read the most recent task file `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json` and confirmed it is already completed\n- [x] Searched all task JSON files for pending tasks, found no pending tasks before 20260407\n- [x] Confirmed no pending tasks needed attention on initial check, replied HEARTBEAT_OK\n- [x] Found the new pending task: `openclaw_daily_20260407.json`\n- [x] Confirmed the `wechat_articles/` directory exists and contains past daily OpenClaw news articles, including the most recent one from April 6, 2026\n- [x] Read the April 6, 2026 past article `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md` to reference its format\n- [x] Checked git log in workspace and parent directory, confirmed neither is a git repository (check failed as expected)\n- [x] Two `web_search` attempts both failed with a 401 Kimi API authentication error\n- [x] Attempted `web_fetch` to get latest OpenClaw updates from GitHub, which failed\n- [x] Opened a browser instance to access the OpenClaw GitHub repository, navigated to multiple recent pull request pages\n- [x] Captured multiple browser snapshots of GitHub pages\n\n### In Progress\n- Access the full content of recent OpenClaw pull request pages to extract the latest PR/commit news (current snapshot content only shows header navigation, actual PR/commit content is truncated)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **No pending tasks found on initial check**: Confirmed all existing daily tasks before 20260407 are completed, so replied HEARTBEAT_OK per instructions\n- **Switched to alternative access method after API failures**: After `web_search` and `web_fetch` failed to retrieve latest OpenClaw news, used a browser instance to access the OpenClaw GitHub repository directly to get content\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Access the full content of the navigated GitHub pull request pages to extract latest valuable OpenClaw updates\n2. Collect 2-3 latest valuable OpenClaw updates\n3. Write the styled daily news article for April 7, 2026 following the format of past articles\n4. Save the finished article to the `wechat_articles/` directory with a date-named filename\n5. Mark the `openclaw_daily_20260407.json` task as completed\n\n## Critical Context\n- Current check time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 4:22 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 20:22 UTC\n- The most recent completed task `openclaw_daily_20260406.json` (search OpenClaw latest news and generate a WeChat public account article) is already marked as completed\n- No tasks with `\"status\": \"pending\"` were found in `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/*.json` before 20260407\n- The current pending task is `openclaw_daily_20260407.json`: generate a WeChat official account article covering the latest 7-day OpenClaw news, save to `wechat_articles/` with a date-named filename\n- Two `web_search` attempts both failed with a 401 Kimi API authentication error\n- Neither the workspace nor parent directory is a git repository\n- Captured browser snapshots of GitHub PR pages only show header navigation content; actual PR/commit content needed for news extraction is still truncated\n- The goal is to collect 2-3 latest valuable OpenClaw updates and write the styled daily news article for April 7, 2026\n- Read files this session:\n  `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks`\n  `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json`\n  `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260407.json`\n  `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles`\n  `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md`\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260407.json\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"518182de","tokensBefore":25986,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260406.json","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/openclaw_daily_20260407.json","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles","/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/wechat_articles/openclaw_daily_20260406.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":false}
