{"type":"message","id":"bbb020f1","parentId":"d35d0ec9","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:11:55.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了问题！**`local-gpu` 提供商没有配置 API 密钥认证**。错误信息明确给出了原因：\n\n```\nError: No API key found for provider \"local-gpu\". \nAuth store: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json \n(agentDir: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent). \nConfigure auth for this agent (openclaw agents add <id>) or copy auth-profiles.json from the main agentDir.\n```\n\n## 🔍 问题原因\n\n虽然你在配置文件中定义了 `local-gpu` 模型，但是 OpenClaw 的认证系统中没有添加 `local-gpu` 提供商的认证信息，所以每次调用都会失败，自动回落到火山模型。\n\n## 💡 解决方案\n\n你需要执行以下命令添加 `local-gpu` 的认证配置：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw agents add local-gpu\n```\n\n这个命令会引导你配置 `local-gpu` 的认证信息。对于本地 GPU 部署，通常只需要配置 API 端点和（可选的）API 密钥。\n\n让我检查一下当前的 `auth-profiles.json` 文件看看现有的配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2pz342epnvgbv38w76hw7tgh","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":6543,"output":319,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775545908840,"responseId":"021775545908947eff6165463a2ce5f140dae355499e17999138e"}}
