{"type":"message","id":"16e46445","parentId":"de21fe37","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:11:58.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"果然，这里只有 `moonshot:default` 和 `ollama:default`，缺少 `local-gpu` 的认证配置。你需要添加一个 `local-gpu` 的认证 profile。\n\n让我帮你看看 `local-gpu` 的模型配置是什么样的，确认一下 API endpoint：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_uotlzg5adp30hctka3uogtxw","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.get","path":"models.providers.local-gpu"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":7615,"output":118,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31597,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775545915069,"responseId":"021775545915181eff6165463a2ce5f140dae355499e179478c62"}}
