{"type":"message","id":"c164782e","parentId":"bcd4913d","timestamp":"2026-04-07T07:12:31.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ **问题已经修复！** 现在 qwen3.5 35b 模型应该可以正常使用了。\n\n## 🔍 问题原因\n\n错误信息显示：\n```\nError: No API key found for provider \"local-gpu\". \nAuth store: /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/auth-profiles.json\n```\n\nOpenClaw 的认证系统要求每个提供商都必须在 `auth-profiles.json` 中配置认证信息，即使 `apiKey` 是空的也要添加 profile 记录。之前只有 `moonshot` 和 `ollama`，缺少 `local-gpu` 的记录，所以每次调用都会失败，自动回落到火山引擎模型。\n\n## ✅ 修复内容\n\n1. **添加了** `local-gpu:default` 认证 profile\n2. **更新了** `lastGood` 配置，指定默认使用 `local-gpu:default`\n3. **已重启网关** 让配置生效\n\n现在你可以切换到 `qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b` 模型测试了：\n```\n/session model qwen/qwen3.5-35b-a3b\n```\n\n如果还有问题可以随时告诉我！😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":634,"output":273,"cacheRead":27448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28355,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775545946675,"responseId":"021775545946794eff6165463a2ce5f140dae355499e1791a8baa"}}
